<DocsPageLead>
    Loop a series of images or texts in a limited space.
</DocsPageLead>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    The <Code>Carousel</Code> component is used to display large numbers of visual content on a rotating timer. It also includes support for previous/next controls and indicators.
</DocsPageParagraph>

